reviewText: The CD collection came rapidly and well packed in time for my husband's anniversary gift from me.  He kept watching the commercials,laughing and wishing he had the money to purchase the entire set.  We watched these shows years ago and can't wait to laugh with them again.  Even though I received my order a couple of weeks ago,  I just gave the gift to my husband.  For that reason,  we haven't  started to view the CDs, but if there is any problem with any of them I know, as in the past,  I will be able to make a return.
